verbose_text: Notably, although the nuclear levels of Pap1 appeared similar in Deltatrx1Deltatxl1 and Deltatrr1 cells (XREF_FIG B), a significantly smaller proportion of Pap1 was oxidized in Deltatrx1Deltatxl1 cells compared with either Deltatrr1 or wild-type cells treated with H 2 O 2 (XREF_FIG A and 3C).
